==English==

===Pronunciation===
back·gamm·on
*AHD: /bākgāmōn/

===Noun===
'''backgammon'''
# A [[board game]] for two [[player]]s in which each has 15 [[piece]]s which move between 24 [[triangle|triangular]] spaces [[according]] to the roll of a [[pair]] of [[dice]]; the [[object]] is to move all your pieces around, and off the board.

